    "Using the two GPT industrial chatbot versions, we test the backend results of the auto-parameter configuration in an I5.0 context.",
    "Unlike in our I4.0 model [53], where the only condition for running overtime was to check the final product count level, we design five prompts, presented in Table 2, based on I5.0 basic requirements to determine how the system can optimally reach its target by generating auto-parameters while prioritizing factory operators and ecosystem safety.We present in Figs.",
